## Edge Cases / Pointy Bits

### Modal
- What if modal content is taller than viewport? (scrollable body)
- What if two modals try to open simultaneously? (queue or prevent)
- What about nested modals? (generally avoid, but handle gracefully)

### Dropdown
- Dropdown near edge of screen? (flip direction)
- Very long dropdown menu? (max-height with scroll)
- Dropdown inside a scrolling container? (position issues)

### Table
- Empty data set? (show empty state, not broken table)
- 1000+ rows? (virtualization or warn about performance)
- Column with very long text? (truncate with tooltip)
- Sort on column with mixed types? (consistent behavior)

### Data Fixtures
- What if JSON is malformed? (graceful error, not crash)
- What if required field missing? (default values)

