## Edge Cases / Pointy Bits

### Dashboard
- What if ALL attention items are zero? (show "All clear!" state)
- What if activity feed is empty? (show "No recent activity")
- Network error loading stats? (show error state, not broken page)

### Organizations List
- Search with special characters? (escape regex, don't crash)
- Filter combination returns zero results? (clear empty state)
- Very long organization name? (truncate with ellipsis + tooltip)
- Rapid filter changes? (debounce to avoid performance issues)

### Organization Detail
- Invalid org ID in URL? (404 page or redirect)
- Org with no licenses? (empty state in Licenses tab)
- Org with no billing account? (prompt to create one)

### Impersonation
- What if impersonated org is deleted? (clear state, show message)
- Admin impersonating then logging out? (clear impersonation state)
- Multiple tabs with different impersonation states? (sync via localStorage event)

